around Yanglou Street.

57
00:02:37,110 --> 00:02:39,000
I bet their house was in that neighborhood.

58
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:42,520
Later, Ms. Wu opened the Wu's Restaurant.

59
00:02:42,670 --> 00:02:44,650
I remember it happened only two years ago.

60
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:46,360
So, could Sun Bo buy us the bao

61
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,840
- that have left a deep impression on me - Thank you.

62
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:49,390
from old Mr. Wu?

63
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,950
Come to think of it,

64
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:53,110
Sun Bo's house was

65
00:02:53,550 --> 00:02:55,310
in Yanglou Street at that time.

66
00:02:57,550 --> 00:02:58,750
What have you thought of?

67
00:02:58,750 --> 00:03:00,590
If Sun Bo was living in that neighborhood,

68
00:03:00,670 --> 00:03:02,640
he and the siblings of Wu's family

69
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:04,000
should have known each other for long.

70
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:07,720
So what?

71
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:09,110
If they have known each other for long,

72
00:03:09,190 --> 00:03:10,310
when Wu Qiao killed her brother,

73
00:03:10,390 --> 00:03:12,110
Sun Bo may have lent her a hand.

74
00:03:12,110 --> 00:03:13,190
What do you mean?

75
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,470
The Hat Demon.

76
00:03:14,590 --> 00:03:15,360
The Hat Demon?

77
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:17,920
